凡脊瓜柱以步架加舉定高。如步架深五尺五寸。按九举加之得高四尺九寸五分。內除三架梁高一尺八寸八分。得脊瓜柱淨高三尺七分。外加平水
高一尺。又加桁条径三分之一作桁碗。得三寸三分。
The height of the ridge guazhu post determined using the dimension [of the relevant]“ju.” If the bu spans a distance of [550 fen] at 9 ju, the height
of ridge guazhu is [495 fen] (90% of 550). From the dimension of the 9 ju (90% of the 脊步=495 fen) subtract the height of the the 3-purlin beam (188
fen) and you will attain“net height”(淨高) of the ridge guazhu, which is [307 fen]. To this height add the dimension of “pingshui” (100 fen) and the
height of “hengwan,” (lit. purlin bowl) which is 1/3 the diameter of the ridge purlin [33 fen].
